Firmware upgrades in Pure Storage environments are typically non-disruptive due to the architecture of Pure arrays. The upgrade process involves planning the upgrade window, ensuring backups are up to date, and following Pure Storageâ€™s documented procedures. Pure Storage support can assist with the upgrade to ensure it proceeds smoothly.
	
	
	1. Administration --> Edge Services --> Request Access
	2. CLI
	#Puresupport enable edge-mgmt
	#puresupport enable edge-agent-update
	3. Pure1 --> Purity/FA Upgrade agent
	Install FA Agent
	
